Package service

package service
It is the package representation of the Service layer.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    service.dto
    It contains the class definitions of the DTO classes, which are used by the front-end/viewcontroller and the Service layers.
    service.exceptions
    It contains the exception definitions for Service-layer operations.

    The CustomerServiceImpl class implements the methods defined in the IService interface for the Customer primary table.

    The IService interface contains the Service-level definitions of the CRUD wrapper methods and common metrics.
